abstract: The final regular-season game of the M.L.S. season will decide the postseason matchups.
snippet: The final regular-season game of the M.L.S. season will decide the postseason matchups.
lead_paragraph: The result of Sunday night's Houston-Los Angeles match (7 p.m. Eastern, Galavision), the last regular-season match of the Major League Soccer season, will settle the postseason matchups.
